description:
This art was born when I was rejected by the state university that I aspired to be, the emotions that I can pour into this art.

The feeling of confusion because the road that has been laid out neatly must be messy and must assemble a new path is well described by the object of the confused person in this art.

Loneliness can also be described well with this work, I am very relieved when this art can be created because my emotions have moved to this art and I perpetuate that feeling in this art, when I saw it I remember very well how disappointed I was at that time.

But as we all see, in this art there is water that is always moving, indicating that time will always run and I must live this life to the fullest.

Thank you.
